p: As per the previously mentioned results, Ht-EAF exhibited the strongest radical scavenging ability and fascinating anti-diabetic effects. It might be due to the massive accumulation of bioactive compounds. Hence, Ht-EAF was utilized for the UPLC-QTOF-MS/MS analysis, and the findings are presented with tentatively identified phytocompounds along with formula, RT (min), m/ z [M-H] âˆ’, mass error (ppm), response and fragmentation ( m/ z) ( Figure 5 and Table 2).
